<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1436,1758,2035]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
The first report about a not pit-building antlion larva regards almost surely this species (
<bibRefCitation author="Reaumur, R. A. F. de" box="[1168,1341,1758,1783]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" refId="ref41772" refString="Reaumur, R. A. F. de (1742) Histoire des Formica-leo. Memoires pour servir a l'histoire des insectes. Vol. 6. Paris, pp. 333 - 386." type="book" year="1742">Réaumur 1742</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Bonnet, C." pageId="23" pageNumber="24" pagination="277 - 289" refId="ref38888" refString="Bonnet, C. (1780) Oeuvres d'histoire naturelle et de philosophie. Vol. 2. cfr. Marc-Michel Rey, Amsterdam, pp. 277 - 289." type="book chapter" year="1780">Bonnet 1780</bibRefCitation>
) but the first accurate scientific description was realized much later by 
<bibRefCitation author="Brauer, F." box="[1036,1198,1794,1819]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" pagination="463 - 472" refId="ref38958" refString="Brauer, F. (1854) Beitrage zur Kenntniss des inneren Baues und der Verwandlung der Neuropteren. Verhandlungen des Zoologisch-Botanischen Vereins in Wien, 4, 463 - 472." type="journal article" year="1854">Brauer (1854)</bibRefCitation>
, subsequently it was redescribed many times (
<bibRefCitation author="Hagen, H. A." box="[431,572,1830,1855]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" pagination="377 - 398" refId="ref39945" refString="Hagen, H. A. (1873) Die Larven von Myrmeleon. Stettiner Entomologische Zeitung, 34, 249 - 295, 377 - 398." type="journal article" year="1873">Hagen 1873</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Redtenbacher, J." box="[584,805,1830,1855]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" pagination="335 - 368" refId="ref41745" refString="Redtenbacher, J. (1884) Ubersicht der Myrmeleoniden-Larven. Denkschriften, Akademie der Wissenschaften Wien, Mathematische-Naturwissenschaftliche Klasse, 48, 335 - 368." type="journal article" year="1884">Redtenbacher 1884</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Steffan, J. R." box="[816,961,1830,1855]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" pagination="383 - 410" refId="ref42526" refString="Steffan, J. R. (1975) Les larves de Fourmilions [Planipennes: Myrmeleontidae] de la faune de France. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France (N. S.), 11, 383 - 410." type="journal article" year="1975">Steffan 1975</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Satar, A. &amp; Suludere, Z. &amp; Canbulat, S. &amp; Ozbay, C." box="[973,1160,1830,1855]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" pagination="57 - 64" refId="ref41963" refString="Satar, A., Suludere, Z., Canbulat, S. &amp; Ozbay, C. (2006) Rearing the larval stages of Distoleon tetragrammicus (Fabricius, 1798) (Neuroptera: Myrmeleontidae) from egg to adult, with notes on their behaviour. Zootaxa, 1371, 57 - 64." type="journal article" year="2006">
Satar 
<emphasis box="[1038,1094,1830,1855]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Krivokhatsky, V. A." box="[1171,1389,1830,1855]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" refId="ref40265" refString="Krivokhatsky, V. A. (2011) Antlions (Neuroptera: Myrmeleontidae) of Russia. KMK, Saint Petersburg, Russia, 334 pp." type="book" year="2011">Krivokhatsky 2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
